thread.title: Enbridge says will not speculate on Line 9 in-service date
thread.title_full: Enbridge says will not speculate on Line 9 in-service date | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Enbridge says will not speculate on Line 9 in-service date
text:
CALGARY, Alberta, Sept 30 Enbridge Inc said on Wednesday it did not have a specific date for return to full service for the newly-reversed Line 9 pipeline, after Canadian regulators gave the delayed project the green light.
"There are still some technical preparations that are required and line-fill is not an exactly timed process, so we will not speculate at this time on a specific date for return to full service," Enbridge spokesman Graham White said. (Reporting by Nia Williams; Editing by Chris Reese )
